otlib and Seaborn.',NULL,'intermediate','published',5,'2026-01-02 05:19:18','2026-01-02 05:19:18',NULL,NULL,'open',1,1,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1,'Practical Projects','python-practical-projects','Build real-world Python projects including CLI tools, web scraping, database applications, automation scripts, and API development.',NULL,'intermediate','published',6,'2026-01-02 05:19:18','2026-01-02 05:19:18',NULL,NULL,'open',1,1,NULL,NULL,NULL),(9,1,'Best Practices and Design Patterns','python-best-practices','Learn Python best practices, code quality, PEP 8, documentation, design patterns, and software architecture for large projects.',NULL,'advanced','published',7,'2026-01-02 05:19:18','2026-01-02 05:19:18',NULL,NULL,'open',1,1,NULL,NULL,NULL);
